
1. Intro

        ****** Under Construction ******

2. Installation - dependencies

        * Ubuntu (12.04)

        $ sudo apt-get install libpcap-dev libpcap0.8 libpcap0.8-dev
        $ sudo apt-get install tshark

        * Fedora (18)

        $ sudo yum install libpcap.x86_64 libpcap-devel.x86_64
        $ sudo yum install wireshark

3. Compilation

        $ gcc ip-file.c -lpcap -o op-file.op
        # lpcap -> libpcap lib
